{"tid":637212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年漢骨場按摩 突然昏迷送院亡","createTime":"2018-04-21T14:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T08:52:24.000Z","uid":157545,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"87d47e28daf53c7b7946566dc3e206bb8cb86769","tid":637212,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/photo/bkn-20180421200036637-0421_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180421222019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180421200036637-0421_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180421222019&h=4148a8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角中年男骨場內暈倒送院死亡。現場為旺角弼街38至44A號利發大廈，傍晚6時許，一名姓陳(42歲)男子到上址按摩場所，約20分鐘後，當技師為他服務之際，陳突然胸口痛，身體開始抽搐，未幾更暈倒昏迷，在場職員報案。<br />\n<br />\n救護員趕至現場，將事主送院搶救，惜終告不治，警員到場調查事件，不排除事主病發猝死，惟確切死因有待驗屍確定。警方已聯絡陳的家人助查，據知，有人曾表示心跳快不適，但一直未有求醫。"},{"pid":"b6f2aac077a7b171f503e0bd3f3f9d846f5cc5c6","tid":637212,"uid":161741,"like":131,"dislike":3,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"馬上風"},{"pid":"839f51ecaa14865ff5ad1a17719883572ec5d81c","tid":637212,"uid":19462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"性急 無帶脷底丸 咁就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1214a19417423cfac0ab94a04a39bfe518698ceb","tid":637212,"uid":65984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"精盡人亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285db0a0fe1c4067a0e912eefa9ef09335518730","tid":637212,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"最佳死亡方法"},{"pid":"1a3bfdac19b847699a0fa930ac56c12a758b38a1","tid":637212,"uid":92714,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"金帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb272264ad84af7355f2f